sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User
    participant System as System

    User->>System: Send self-destructing message
    System-->>User: Acknowledge message sent
    System->>User: Notify message will self-destruct
    User->>System: Read message
    System-->>User: Display message content
    Note over User, System: Message self-destructs after viewing
    System->>User: Confirm message deleted